summary: We can try to fight someone else’s battles. We can do it by sacrificing ourselves and neglecting our journey thinking we will...
body: We can try to fight someone else’s battles. We can do it by sacrificing ourselves and neglecting our journey thinking we will fail the person we love if we’re not standing with them. But forgetting to care for ourselves for the sake of someone else is not love. Love is supposed to bring inner peace. We must be stable and strong enough for ourselves only then will we be strong for others.
